620
00:41:12,159 --> 00:41:13,769
I think that's cooler too.

621
00:41:14,199 --> 00:41:16,329
Who says you have to be a worker for life?

622
00:41:16,769 --> 00:41:17,809
Maybe one day,

623
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:19,329
I'll quit and start my own business.

624
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:22,329
Whether or not I'll invest in it is still uncertain.

625
00:41:23,679 --> 00:41:25,559
Let's just wait and see.

